      • killProcess

        public static java.util.List<GenericProcessMonitor.ProcessInfo> killProcess(java.lang.String host,
                                                                            java.lang.String processName,
                                                                            java.lang.String commandline)
                                                                     throws SAFSException
        Kill the process according to the process name and partial command line.
        Parameters:
        host - String, the name of machine on which the process will be killed.
        processName - String, the name of process to kill. like chromedriver.exe, IEDriverServer.exe, java.exe etc.
        commandline - String, the partial commandline of the process to be killed.
        Returns:
        List, a list containing the killed process's id and kill-execution-return-code.
        Throws:
        SAFSException

      • killProcess

        public static java.util.List<GenericProcessMonitor.ProcessInfo> killProcess(java.lang.String host,
                                                                            java.lang.String processName,
                                                                            java.lang.String commandline,
                                                                            java.lang.String notCommandline)
                                                                     throws SAFSException
        Kill the process according to the process name and partial command line.
        Parameters:
        host - String, the name of machine on which the process will be killed.
        processName - String, the name of process to kill. like chromedriver.exe, IEDriverServer.exe, java.exe etc.
        commandline - String, the partial commandline of the process to be killed.
        notCommandline - String, the partial commandline of the process NOT to be killed.
        Returns:
        List, a list containing the killed process's id and kill-execution-return-code.
        Throws:
        SAFSException
